        "description": {
            "value": "<p>This potent poison consists of crystals whose flavor and appearance mimics edible salt but whose effects are deadly: victims experience periods of waking nightmares that overload the senses and eventually result in death through a combination of shock and exhaustion.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 'Pathfinder2eActions'; font-size: 1.8em; display: inline;\">T</span>&nbsp;Interact (Ingested)</p>\n<p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> DC 43 Fortitude</p>\n<p><strong>Onset</strong> 1 hour</p>\n<p><strong>Maximum Duration</strong> 5 days</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.TBSHQspnbcqxsmjL]{Frightened} 2 once every [[/r 1d4]] hours, plus @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.HL2l2VRSaQHu9lUw]{Fatigued} (1 day)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.yblD8fOR1J8rDwEQ]{Confused} for 1 minute once every [[/r 1d4]] hours, plus frightened 3 and fatigued (1 day)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 3</strong> frightened 3, plus confused for [[/r 1d4]] minutes, once every hour, plus fatigued (1 day)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 4</strong> death</p>",
